bb763","tid":106582,"uid":35357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T09:34:33.000Z","msg":"有，幾年前開始咁諗<br />\n<br />\n生老病死，我想skip左病<br />\n50，60歲左右就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f055ecb314ef44ec0586ef393fcfbc8d1ff2408","tid":106582,"uid":47160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T09:41:52.000Z","msg":"個世界咁多野玩你有錢一定唔會玩厭<br />\n就算普通平民一樣有好多低消費甚至免費既娛樂俾你選擇<br />\n好難話幾時玩夠"},{"pid":"e906efcdbac75ad7a1c1f7d083e671b0f152cacc","tid":106582,"uid":39725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T11:31:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有，幾年前開始咁諗<br />\n<br />\n生老病死，我想skip左病<br />\n50，60歲左右就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗作為絲打最怕就係自己人老珠黃俾人唾棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老公去叫雞或者包二奶，搞散頭家<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到有病仲慘"},{"pid":"efa0219afe3eb7285a6b7199d7621e509fb51d9b","tid":106582,"uid":39725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T11:32:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個世界咁多野玩你有錢一定唔會玩厭<br />\n就算普通平民一樣有好多低消費甚至免費既娛樂俾你選擇<br />\n好難話幾時玩夠</blockquote><br />\n我諗係我放錯咗生活重心喺唔岩嘅地方呱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我會為自己做多啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />增值自己"},{"pid":"756fa9d1e0f947de6a5d6c0b7ae1aca73e557368","tid":106582,"uid":1424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T11:33:42.000Z","msg":"覺<br />\n我接受唔到自己五六十歲多病痛，妹下妹下咁，嘢又唔食得d 乜，又邊度都去唔到去唔遠咁"},{"pid":"899503b8f2d1325055eb975de2fc632061cb4553","tid":106582,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T12:35:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺<br />\n我接受唔到自己五六十歲多病痛，妹下妹下咁，嘢又唔食得d 乜，又邊度都去唔到去唔遠咁</blockquote><br />\n其實六十歲唔係好似你想像中咁老，我父母六十歲都仲好健康"},{"pid":"4d3dbd645aeb1b6730258054500c55ce53bc7d70","tid":106582,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T14:46:29.000Z","msg":"接受唔到40歲之後既自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b260fd3a64fee326887858021c8bc623bc95308d","tid":106582,"uid":81222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T14:50:01.000Z","msg":"成日都有咁嘅想法<br />\n覺得快啲死咗咪好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔洗再面對啲咩煩惱同壓力<br />\n做人好似無咩意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0125384683290053bb1550e820069ed39610fe6e","tid":106582,"uid":5122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T15:07:46.000Z","msg":"人類有無窮無盡嘅欲望 永遠都滿足唔哂 所以當你滿足哂社會所界定嘅美滿生活時 你就會想要更多 享受更耐<br />\n咁即係話 永遠你都會唔捨得死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab7497504f50d0ffe5c44c21b2067cc3c2cafdfa","tid":106582,"uid":39725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T15:19:48.000Z","msg":"大家好似唔明嗰種唔想走下坡嘅心情咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dafbf37492b851644adaa6778840dda424b4bbaf","tid":106582,"uid":35357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T15:20:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有，幾年前開始咁諗<br />\n<br />\n生老病死，我想skip左病<br />\n50，60歲左右就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗作為絲打最怕就係自己人老珠黃俾人唾棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老公去叫雞或者包二奶，搞散頭家<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到有病仲慘</blockquote><br />\n我係唔想比疾病折磨<br />\n但我一定會等雙親走哂先再諗"},{"pid":"43aac550c79e023db796725640d1d14845262653","tid":106582,"uid":39725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T15:21:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日都有咁嘅想法<br />\n覺得快啲死咗咪好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔洗再面對啲咩煩惱同壓力<br />\n做人好似無咩意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都有啲覺得做人好煩，我廿幾歲已經覺得好多野唔係自己做得好件事就會好，<br />\n有時好唔開心，覺得點解人地要咁對我，明明自己平時待人唔差，好難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋我好怕孤獨，唔想得返自己一個人"},{"pid":"c17227dccc5bde4dbc0e1b768b0d6f25bc84195b","tid":106582,"uid":60402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T15:22:43.000Z","msg":"李小龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a6191bc3269380f3d88f1f5dc2026b62b44edcd","tid":106582,"uid":68971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T15:25:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你唔行哂成個人生永遠唔知global maximum係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁呀&hellip; 咁可能係普遍人想要嘅野可能已經有晒，<br />\n姐係可能事業有成，屋企又美滿，人生已經開心到不能再開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者叫已經係達到self achievement嗰個level?</blockquote><br />\n但如果係依個時候結束自己既生命<br />\n咁依段美滿時刻仲叫唔叫美滿<br />\n已經因為失去左你存在而產生缺陷"},{"pid":"d5b8c280a10dda6c3e7dffed7b1033256e4348a8","tid":106582,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T15:32:44.000Z","msg":"請支持爭取安樂死"},{"pid":"9fdb47a2b386b45aad0f85505b9e01db309e74e5","tid":106582,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T15:36:00.000Z","msg":"之前睇到日本有單新聞就係有個十四歲女仔話自己好開心所以走左去自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05d468d91882b3cee5f99563d8dc5e2717498f62","tid":106582,"uid":9962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T15:46:07.000Z","msg":"我明，我20歲嘅parttime已經帶住一班義工搞活動比小朋友、老人家，教佢地些少輔導技巧；負責排更表、寫計劃書交上政府攞資助，成間中心都好認同我，支持我..但我唔係想讚自己有幾叻。<br />\n因為我而家只係返朝9晚8 濕尻工，比個守舊又官僚主義嘅老闆騎住.. 以前嘅衝勁冇晒，創意冇晒，連同人講野都唔夠膽望住人.. 我覺得個落差大太，以後我都上唔返以前嘅高峰.. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c974ab11bf9e1fd14a5a3e5d5de9bc38f312cfae","tid":106582,"uid":39725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:12:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前睇到日本有單新聞就係有個十四歲女仔話自己好開心所以走左去自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係呢種，我覺得唔係個個人理解到，<br />\n究竟係啲人唔理解我地點解承受唔到fade away, <br />\n定係我地自己諗法上有缺陷"},{"pid":"6cf6b59fa993dee92446c8653a5384108d1664bc","tid":106582,"uid":71755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:12:19.000Z","msg":"你又知你而家就喺你人生最美滿嘅時候？"},{"pid":"da39a5d17f4dc814233021e9a6bf1270eadad74a","tid":106582,"uid":9962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:12:50.000Z","msg":"我諗樓主係果種想充實自己，但係對物質生活冇乜要求嘅人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"270cbf2886974b4a992cc8bd841cd2f9f1d67edf","tid":106582,"uid":9962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:13:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你又知你而家就喺你人生最美滿嘅時候？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n或者你唔明，其實我地係對將來冇乜信心"},{"pid":"3f785eab5d4662dc011fe68dee017b3334b56cb0","tid":106582,"uid":39725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:13:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你唔行哂成個人生永遠唔知global maximum係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁呀&hellip; 咁可能係普遍人想要嘅野可能已經有晒，<br />\n姐係可能事業有成，屋企又美滿，人生已經開心到不能再開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者叫已經係達到self achievement嗰個level?</blockquote><br />\n但如果係依個時候結束自己既生命<br />\n咁依段美滿時刻仲叫唔叫美滿<br />\n已經因為失去左你存在而產生缺陷</blockquote><br />\n我淨係喺自己嘅角度睇喳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時我都死咗，我嘅人生就完咗，唔會再缺陷啦，只是早咗完姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b9a65b473433287c5cf1cfcc464f6880770e22b","tid":106582,"uid":39725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:16:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我明，我20歲嘅parttime已經帶住一班義工搞活動比小朋友、老人家，教佢地些少輔導技巧；負責排更表、寫計劃書交上政府攞資助，成間中心都好認同我，支持我..但我唔係想讚自己有幾叻。<br />\n因為我而家只係返朝9晚8 濕尻工，比個守舊又官僚主義嘅老闆騎住.. 以前嘅衝勁冇晒，創意冇晒，連同人講野都唔夠膽望住人.. 我覺得個落差大太，以後我都上唔返以前嘅高峰.. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n爸打，我諗你嗰時份part time就係做到self achievement了，<br />\n而而家就好似fade away, 或者有少少走下坡，<br />\n係心靈上嗰種不滿足同埋落差，<br />\n我好明白，我就係唔想承受呢種落差，其實而家冇野發生，<br />\n生活好好，只係我諗緊第時嘅野邊個知，<br />\n我諗到如果變差或者要失去嘅話我就好擔心了"},{"pid":"dd20faa130260ef41e34308d1a048b576deff079","tid":106582,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:17:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你唔行哂成個人生永遠唔知global maximum係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁呀&hellip; 咁可能係普遍人想要嘅野可能已經有晒，<br />\n姐係可能事業有成，屋企又美滿，人生已經開心到不能再開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者叫已經係達到self achievement嗰個level?</blockquote><br />\n但如果係依個時候結束自己既生命<br />\n咁依段美滿時刻仲叫唔叫美滿<br />\n已經因為失去左你存在而產生缺陷</blockquote><br />\n我淨係喺自己嘅角度睇喳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時我都死咗，我嘅人生就完咗，唔會再缺陷啦，只是早咗完姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nLike a piece of art，short but perfect<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00205c755f2439dd84459820da82f12993b299b","tid":106582,"uid":39725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:20:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我諗樓主係果種想充實自己，但係對物質生活冇乜要求嘅人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都算係，世界好大，人好覆雜，<br />\n我覺得自己算係有故事嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申20頭"},{"pid":"5bb18666ed34d52cd7090895c2b22b49238cd128","tid":106582,"uid":39725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:21:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你又知你而家就喺你人生最美滿嘅時候？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n或者你唔明，其實我地係對將來冇乜信心</blockquote><br />\n冇錯呀，可能我渣ga,<br />\n經唔起失去同挫折，淨係諗已經覺得好難受"},{"pid":"de56665d611f5a97df0ad3812894759ad654ede5","tid":106582,"uid":9962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:29:01.000Z","msg":"覆左你之後我真係覺得好難受.. 我睇唔到將來嘅生活可以令我學到乜野。心靈上得唔到進步好辛苦.. 區區物質生活唔算係乜野，遲早都會消逝"},{"pid":"2b0307d3b8aba791d48c850184e1ce01b76045f9","tid":106582,"uid":25201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:31:39.000Z","msg":"最低點就會反彈 呢家係考驗緊你"},{"pid":"6ad717973c3469c653256fdd2ffc43ac1e3385bb","tid":106582,"uid":43651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:35:04.000Z","msg":"會 宜家覺得大概5-60歲可以完結<br />\n當我想做既事 例如結婚生仔去旅行 都完成<br />\n而且係我體力下降再都做唔到呢d個陣 生命就可以完結<br />\n<br />\n唔想做一個廢老 唔想經歷病痛 唔想做人負累 <br />\n<br />\n將來會唔會想睇住仔女結婚生仔湊孫係後話 但宜家係咁諗 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"264132d93351bf1598289b1bf990404d9d098053","tid":106582,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:42:45.000Z","msg":"之前荷蘭先話想放寬安樂死的要求<br />\n只要覺得自己已經活得好足夠就可以申請安樂死<br />\n即係想死就死啦"},{"pid":"d4a435607a2154d2b312f713312dd8f16a8fd007","tid":106582,"uid":67056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:43:45.000Z","msg":"完全明白呢種諗法<br />\n不過我直頭連人生最頂盛嘅位都少有<br />\n天生身體差成日病<br />\n無咩可以引起我興趣<br />\n我會試好多唔同嘅嘢 不過唔會覺得開心或者想keep住<br />\n朋友呢樣野可有可無<br />\n對我嚟講 生存只係為咗等死<br />\n每當有最美滿嘅時刻都好想freeze係個一瞬間"}]}